title: 001: Female Fitness Myths Exposed!
description: Women have been (and continue to be) fed a load of sh&t about fitness and fat loss. If you want to achieve a lean hard body it is time to stop following advice that wastes your time and slows your progress. Sal, Adam & Justin have trained hundreds of women and provide the answers you really need.
